condition shown in Eq. 8. To this end, assume that XÌ‚ âˆˆ â„¦Ì‚(i, j), where â„¦Ì‚(i, j) denote a grid
block at time t = nâˆ†t, whose node is XÌ‚(i, j). Also, at this time t, consider the nearest blocks.
For example, if â„¦Ì‚(i, j) is an inner block, then consider the four neighboring blocks â„¦Ì‚(i + 1, j),
